title: Vuelta a España Stage 21: Record-Equaling Primož Roglič Seals Fourth GC Title, Küng Aces Time Trial
content:
Stefan Küng wins first grand tour stage in final time trial as Ben O’Connor secures second overall ahead of Enric Mas.
